     <pb n="134v" facs="AVN_B_101.01.01.007_0134v"/> 
     <div><head><lb/><choice><abbr>Dud</abbr><expan>Dudit</expan></choice> jour en <orgName ref="org003085">Conseil estroict</orgName>.</head></div>
     <div>
      <p>
       <lb/>Accordé un point de coustume a <persName ref="per011311a.01">Jehan Fornachon</persName>
       <lb/>de <placeName ref="loc007800.02"><choice><abbr>S<hi rend="sup">t</hi></abbr><expan>Saint</expan></choice> Blaise</placeName> touchant l’usufruict qu’un mary
       <lb/>peut jouir des biens de sa femme ni ayant
       <lb/>point d’enfans vivants.
      </p>
